<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-03-04T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-03-01T01:36:00-05:00" n="1148" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1148">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.52/2.</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Ambassador</gloss>
                                    to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                                        <hi rend="italic">Mexico</hi>
                                    </placeName> (<date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1913-03-04T23:59:59-05:00" notBefore="1913-03-01T00:00:00-06:36"><hi rend="italic">not
                                            dated</hi></date><hi rend="italic">; received March 4,
                                        1913</hi>).</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>73. I have instructed the Consul at Piedras Negras (Ciudad Porfirio
                                Diaz), Coahuila, to give to Spanish subjects in his district such
                                protection as may be consistent and necessary. This action is taken
                                at the request of the Spanish Minister.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>. <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>.</signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>